data.description: Nestled in a quiet Warren neighborhood, this brick faced ranch offers up a desirable three-bedroom layout with a partially finished full basement! The attractive residence is surrounded by manicured landscaping as it continues around relaxing rear patio and into the backyard. Here, a detached garage joins a stained wood storage shed. Around the front, a brick sidewalk leads up to the picket lined stairs. Inside, a carpeted living room enjoys a beautifully dressed picture window that illuminates the wood paneled accent wall and nearby dining room. The tall arched ceiling slopes down across the kitchen and its faux brick work that accents the piano black appliances and stained wood cabinets. Opposite dining, additional countertop space enjoys a butcher’s block styled top. An oversized, pass through bath bridges the main hallway, showcasing an oversized, floor entry tiled shower. The trio of inviting bedrooms complete the floor as they branch from the hall. Downstairs, a finished lower family room offsets storage and laundry services.FHA VA Cash Conventional
